data.description: Stunning and meticulously maintained, this OPEN CONCEPT residence is nestled in the charming Terrace Brook community, conveniently situated near major thoroughfares 290, 249, and Beltway 8. Enter the spacious living room with beautiful tall windows that fill the home with natural light, The main level also features a half bath, a convenient laundry room, a well-appointed kitchen, and the master suite. The master bedroom offers a tranquil retreat, while the master bathroom boasts dual vanities, a rejuvenating shower, a soothing jacuzzi tub, and an expansive walk-in closet. Ascending to the upper level, you'll discover three generously sized bedrooms, a full bathroom and a game room. Enhancing the allure of this exceptional home is a beautiful yard, graced by a standby ELECTRIC GENERATOR for added peace of mind. ENHANCEMENTS INCLUDE new blinds, new carpeting, and a fresh coat of paint throughout, water filter, culminating in an inviting and move-in-ready environment.
